doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    title Dummy Course
    style       
        include ../../public/css/course.css
  body
    
    .container
      .sidebar
        h1 Lecture List
        ul#video-list
          li(data-video='./videos/1.mkv') Introduction to Applied Physics
          li(data-video='./videos/2.mkv') UNIT 1
          li(data-video='./videos/3.mkv') UNIT 2
          li(data-video='./videos/4.mkv') UNIT 3
          li(data-video='./videos/5.mkv') UNIT 4
          li(data-video='./videos/6.mkv') Conclusion
      .main-content
        .video-player
          video#video-player(controls='')
            | Your browser does not support the video tag.
          //
            <div class="controls">
            <button id="play-pause-btn">&#9658;</button>
            <input id="seek-bar" type="range" min="0" value="0">
            <button id="mute-btn">&#128266;</button>
            <input id="volume-bar" type="range" min="0" max="1" step="0.1" value="1">
            <button id="fullscreen-btn">&#128470;</button>
            </div>
        .video-description
          .heading(style='max-width: 20vw;')
            h1(style='border-bottom: 3px solid black; padding-bottom: 1px;') Course Description
          p#video-description-text
            | This is a course designed by a P.H.D. professional from DTU who has more than 10 years of teaching experience in this field. This crash course covers all the syllabus in just 10 hours along with some practical demonstration on the topic. After completing this course, you will have an effecient knowledge on the topic. For more such courses, visit the website : 
            a(href="/home")
              span www.Note-O-Hub.com
    script(src='./js/course.js')